<h3 id="mbe插画">MBE插画</h3>
<p>白底上多彩的卡通小元素（一定要描黑边）<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617185067-e382ef41-b448-4023-9de4-95da9ee98222.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=705545&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="立体主义">立体主义</h3>
<p>以许多的角度来描写对象物，各个角度交错迭放造成了许多的垂直与平行的线条角度，散乱的阴影使立体主义的画面没有传统西方绘画的透视法造成的三维空间错觉。<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617207503-5b9bd584-9c04-48f2-814f-a21ca15689df.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=2571630&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="low-poly低模">Low-Poly低模</h3>
<p>建模做出块面感，把一个图片分成四个三角形填充，把每个三角形分成四个小三角形<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617232119-d853b855-6ab0-4e83-a0e9-3199d0dcd8e9.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=2202387&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="剪纸风">剪纸风</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617251531-5cefe587-002e-4eed-914b-580453f12e9d.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=1789792&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="极简风">极简风</h3>
<p>无印良品、优衣库，原研哉，性冷淡<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617276303-72085ddd-0994-4195-a2ee-5ec30e26dc3c.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=698136&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="文字主体">文字主体</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617298066-7d5d5eb5-bceb-41f7-a346-5d9f1adbb712.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=1330432&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="极繁风">极繁风</h3>
<p>大胆的用色；重复的元素；填充整个页面；裁剪和拼贴设计<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617318364-b9a03f2e-00ca-4a2b-9319-e7926914fd99.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=676&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=676&amp;originWidth=1022&amp;size=1011224&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=1022" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="像素风">像素风</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2452046/1613617336648-dbfb60c3-6786-41f3-b3a0-cf49c9c00ff5.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1677&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=Untitled.png&amp;originHeight=1677&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=1838902&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=750" alt="Untitled.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="哥特风">哥特风</h3>
<p>黑暗，孤独，绝望，恐惧，颓废，巫术，吸血鬼<br>
